title: Townhouse Available Now, Open Floor Plan, Family Room, Huge Deck, A/C
posting_body: ['Rosemount Townhouse Available', 'Now, Open Floor Plan, Lower Family Room, Huge Deck, 2 Car Garage', 'Property Address', '14553 Cobalt Ave | Rosemount, MN 55068', 'Available: Now', 'Offered By', 'Guardian Property Management |', 'show contact info', 'Description', 'To apply, go to <URL>  Each adult would apply and upload last two pay statements and proof of other income.', 'Rosemount townhouse available now.', ' Open floor plan on the main level.', ' Living room has a walkout to the large deck.', ' The dining area is between the living room and kitchen.', ' Black and stainless appliances including a microwave and dishwasher.', " There's also a half bathroom on the main level.", 'Both bedrooms are upstairs with a full bathroom in between.', ' The master is large enough for a king set.', 'Small lower family room downstairs, a laundry room and a mud room that connects to the 2 car garage.', ' .', 'SORRY NO PETS', 'Rent includes water/sewer, trash & association dues', '$50 application fee per adult', 'We check income (gross household income must be at least 3 times rent), credit (must be 600 or above), criminal and rental history', 'Call Dakota at', 'show contact info', 'for more information', 'For all units with forced air heating, residents will be enrolled in the Utility & Maintenance Reduction Program at an additional fee of $15 per month.', 'This program ensures that high-quality HVAC filters are regularly delivered to the doorstep, saving our residents 5-15% on energy bills, offers a clean and healthy living environment, and reduces tenant liability.', 'Agent: Dakota DeHaven', 'BROKER: GUARDIAN PROPERTY MANAGEMENT AND SERVICES LLC', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 2BD/1.5BA', 'Square Feet: 1,406', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $1,775.00', 'Available: Now', 'Application Fee: $50.00', 'Security Deposit: $1,775.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats not allowed', 'Dogs not allowed']
